Well, this definitely wasn’t a part of our 1 year anniversary celebration plans.

We are honored and humbled to be nominated for the Best Adaptation Award at #TheGameAwards!

God of War Ragnarök has been nominated for 10 awards at #thegameawards, including Game of the Year!

This has been a remarkable year for gaming with so many incredible releases, we are truly honored to be nominated among such excellent titles!

#GodofWarRagnarok 🐻🐺

I always view #TheGameAwards as a celebration of video games, not a definitive announcement of what game is objectively “best” in any category. If a game you love wasn’t nominated, this is a great time to give them a shoutout! You just don’t need to shit on other games to do so.
